# Optional: force API origin for fetch + media (img/video) src.
# In `npm run dev`, leave unset to use same-origin `/v1/...` (Vite proxies to FastAPI on :8000).
# Set this when the API is on another host/port, or for `npm run build` / static hosting.
# VITE_API_BASE_URL=http://127.0.0.1:8000

# Optional: Firebase web config (shows "Continue with Google" when repo-root .env does not expose firebase to the API).
# Values are in Firebase Console → Project settings → Your apps → Web app. API must still have
# DIRECTOR_FIREBASE_CREDENTIALS_PATH for POST /v1/auth/firebase to succeed.
# VITE_FIREBASE_API_KEY=
# VITE_FIREBASE_AUTH_DOMAIN=
# VITE_FIREBASE_PROJECT_ID=
# VITE_FIREBASE_APP_ID=
